OL,3,CMarch of the Day: Sporting world
OL,4,Cunites for epic MND walking challenge
OL,6,FAround hundred ex-footballers and
OL,7,Ffamily members joined former teammates
OL,8,FStephen Darby and Marcus Stewart on a
OL,9,F175 mile walking challenge in aid of
OL,10,FMotor Neurone Disease.
OL,12,FThe walk started on Friday, 22 March,
OL,13,Fin Bradford and will take in 17
OL,14,Ffootball grounds across West Yorkshire
OL,15,Fand the North West.
OL,17,FThe challenge will pass through Elland
OL,18,FRoad, the Etihad Stadium, Old Trafford
OL,19,Fand Goodison Park, before finishing at
OL,20,FAnfield on Sunday evening.
