OL,3,CMarch of the Day: Sporting world
OL,4,Cunites for epic MND walking challenge
OL,6,FEx-Huddersfield Town's Marcus Stewart
OL,7,Fwas diagnosed with Motor Neurone
OL,8,FDisease (MND) in 2022 and former
OL,9,FBradford and Liverpool defender
OL,10,FStephen Darby has had the condition
OL,11,Fsince 2018.
OL,13,FMotor Neurone Disease is a life-
OL,14,Fshortening, condition affecting the
OL,15,Fbrain and nerves.
OL,17,FSpeaking at the start of the event
OL,18,Fwhich has been dubbed 'March of the
OL,19,FDay,' Marcus told the PA news agency
OL,20,Fit "satisfies me" that there is "hope
OL,21,Ffor people."
