OL,6,FHe said:" I have a voice still and
OL,7,Fstill quite mobile so the message to
OL,8,Fthem is don't give up and we are
OL,9,Ftrying our best to find a cure. I am
OL,10,Fpart of that and I am not giving up.
OL,12,F"Players have to look after each other
OL,13,Fboth on the pitch and after you've
OL,14,Ffinished. It's nice that so many ex
OL,15,Fpros that I have played with and
OL,16,Fhaven't played with are joining in the
OL,17,Ffight."
