OL,4,Cunites for epic MND walking challenge
OL,6,FWalkers will be wearing blue t-shirts
OL,7,Fin support of Stewart for the first
OL,8,Fpart of the walk to Bolton and will
OL,9,Fthen change into red t-shirts with
OL,10,FDarby's name on the back for the rest
OL,11,Fof the walk.
OL,13,FRob Burrow and his wife Lindsey, who
OL,14,Fare no strangers to fundraising
OL,15,Fchallenges, are also taking part and
OL,16,Fexpressed how important it is to raise
OL,17,Fawareness of the condition.
OL,19,FLindsey said:"The more awareness we
OL,20,Fraise, the more funds we raise."
