OL,6,F"It is that community, that football
OL,7,Fcommunity coming together," she added
OL,8,Fsaying how "lovely" it had been
OL,9,Fchatting to people affected by MND.
OL,11,FOther former players will join Stewart
OL,12,Fand Darby along the way in support of
OL,13,Fthe Darby Rimmer Foundation, including
OL,14,FChris Kirkland, Paul Scholes, Dominic
OL,15,FMatteo, Jill Scott and Mick McCarthy -
OL,16,FStewart's former manager at Sunderland.
OL,18,FMcCarthy said: "When something like
OL,19,Fthis happens to two young men like
OL,20,FStephen and Marcus, people rally
OL,21,Faround and generally people are good. "
