OL,6,FStuart McCall was Darby's manager at
OL,7,FBradford and described the former
OL,8,FBantams full-back as a true
OL,9,Fprofessional.
OL,11,FHe said: "Under circumstances he was
OL,12,Fthe best professional I have ever
OL,13,Fmanaged and epitomises everything you
OL,14,Fwant in a player or person. A good
OL,15,Fturn out for a fantastic guy."
